      <div xml:id="timf-adiu">
        <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e117">Adiutorium</head>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e120">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e122">a</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e125">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e129">Homines omnes eque diligendi sunt, sed si omnibus prodesse non possis, hiis
        potissimum subueniendum est qui pro locorum et temporum uel quarumlibet rerum
        opportunitatibus constrictius tibi quasi quadam sorte iunguntur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e129" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e135">Augustinus de doctrina Christiana libro I.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e140">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e142">b</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e145">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e149">Hec lex est diuine prouidencie ut nemo a superioribus adiuuetur ad cognoscendam
        graciam Dei qui non ad eandem puro affectu inferiores adiuuerit.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e149" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e155">Augustinus de uera religione.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e160">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e162">c</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e165">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e169">Iustum consilium est ut qui se a potentiori uult adiuuari, adiuuet et infirmiorem
        in quo est ipse potentior.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e169" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e175">Augustinus de sermone Domini in monte libro I.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e180">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e182">d</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e185">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e189">Nichil sic probat amicum sicut oneris amici portacio.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e189" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e195">Augustinus de uerbis apostoli capitulo XX.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e201">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e203">e</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e206">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e210">Eleganter dictum est cum quis in puteum cecidisset et aqua eum suffocaret, accessit
        alius eo uiso admirans ait: Quomodo huc cecidisti? Obsecro, inquit, cogita quomodo hinc
        me liberes, non quomodo huc ceciderim, queras.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e210" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e216">Augustinus in epistola ad Ieronymum.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e221">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e223">f</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e226">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e230">Non facile inueniuntur in aduersitate presidia que non fuerint in pace
        quesita.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e230" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e236">Augustinus in sermone.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e241">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e243">g</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e246">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e250">Necessitates aliorum quantum possumus iuuemus et plus interdum quam possumus.
        Nichil tam secundum naturam est quam iuuare consortem nature.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e250" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e256">Ambrosius de officiis.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e261">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e263">h</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e266">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e270">Si non potest alteri subueniri nisi alter ledatur, commodius est neutrum iuuari
        quam grauari alterum.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e270" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e276">Ambrosius de officiis libro III.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e281">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e283">i</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e286">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e290">Vult enim Deus unumquemque alterius angustias ut proprias sentire, et quomodo sibi
        in tali tribulacione si esset subueniri cuperet, ita ipse alteri propter Deum subuenire
        non postponat.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e290" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e296">Ieronymus in epistolis.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e301">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e303">k</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e306">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e310">Impudens postulacio tempore necessitatis et angustie ab eo querere auxilium quem in
        prosperitate contempseris.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e310" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e316">Ieronymus super Ieremiam libro I. super illud: In tempore afflictionis dicent surge et
       cetera.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e322">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e324">l</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e327">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e331">Habens loquendi locum apud diuitem, dampnacionem pro retento talento timeat, si non
        apud eum sicut ualet pro pauperibus intercedat.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e331" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e337">Gregorius in omelia.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e342">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e344">m</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e347">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e351">Habens intellectum, curet omnino ne taceat; habens rerum affluenciam, a
        misericordia non torpescat; habens artem qua regitur, usum illius cum proximo parciatur;
        habens loquendi locum apud diuitem, pro pauperibus intercedat. Talenti enim nomine
        cuilibet reputabitur quod eciam minimum accepit.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e351" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e357">Gregorius in quadam omelia.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e362">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e364">n</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e367">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e371">Qui potest emendare et negligit, participem se proculdubio constituit; qui alterius
        bonum adiuuat, suum facit.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e371" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e377">Gregorius in registro.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e382">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e384">o</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e387">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e391">Minus proximum amare conuincitur qui non cum eo in necessitate illius ea que sibi
        sunt necessaria partitur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e391" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e397">Gregorius in omelia.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e402">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e404">p</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e407">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e411">Tunc amor tuus ad te ipsum temperans erit et iustus, si quod propriis subtrahitur
        uoluptatibus fratris necessitatibus non negetur. Sic amor socialis efficitur cum in
        commune protrahitur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e411" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e417">Bernardus de diligendo Deo.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e422">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e424">q</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e427">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e431">Oleum pietatis et miseracionis unguentum quanto copiosius in fraternas necessitates
        effunditur, tanto donis potioribus augmentatur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e431" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e437">Cassiodorus in quadam epistola.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e443">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e445">r</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e448">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e452">Age sic aliud ut tuum non obliuiscaris negocium. Amicis enim ita prodesse debemus
        ut nobis non noceamus.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e452" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e458">Cassiodorus in epistola.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e463">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e465">s</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e468">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e472">Quid tibi, fidelissime, opus sunt arma qui habere talia probaris auxilia? Ipse enim
        pro te pugnat cui nullus resistit; ipse insequitur quem nullus declinat.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e472" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e478">Cassiodorus super Psalmum LV.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e483">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e485">t</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e488">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e492">Gratum debet esse subsidium cuius solucio magis soluenti crescit incommodum quam
        suscipienti proficiat in augmentum, et quod dantem iuuat et accipientem pro temporis
        necessitate letificat ut sic in una mercacione quod raro solet emergere, utrique
        uideantur desiderata commoda percepisse.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e492" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e498">Cassiodorus in quadam epistola.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e503">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e505">u</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e508">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e512">Satis ibi uacillat humanum studium ubi non requiritur Dei auxilium.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e512" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e518">Valerius in quodam sermone.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e523">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e525">x</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e528">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e532">Homini iocundo et probo miserimum est, si eum amare oportet quem non iuuat.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e532" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e538">Seneca de beneficiis.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e543">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e545">y</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e548">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e552">Habet in aduersis auxilia qui in prosperis commodat.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e552" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e558">Seneca in prouerbiis.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e564">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e566">ab</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e569">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e573">Qui succurrere perituro potest, cum non succurrit, occidit.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e573" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e579">Seneca in prouerbiis.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e584">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e586">ac</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e589">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e593">Nemo non cum alteri prodest sibi profuit. Virtutum omnium precium in ipsis est;
        recte facti fecisse merces est.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e593" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e599">Seneca LXXXII. epistola.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e604">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e606">ad</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e609">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e613">Succurre paupertati amicorum stude, immo pocius occurre.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e613" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e619">Seneca in libello de moribus.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e624">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e626">ae</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e629">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e633">Penam a quo merueris, frustra petis auxilium. Ab alio expecta, alteri quod
        feceris.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e633" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e639">Idem (Seneca).</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="timf-adiu-Dd1e644">
          <head xml:id="timf-adiu-Hd1e646">af</head>
          <p xml:id="timf-adiu-d1e649">
            <cit>
              <quote xml:id="timf-adiu-Qd1e653">Fructus ingenii et uirtutis omnisque prestancie, tunc maximus capitur cum in
        proximum quemque confertur.</quote>
              <bibl/>
            </cit>
            <ref corresp="#timf-adiu-Qd1e653" xml:id="timf-adiu-Rd1e659">Tullius de amicicia.</ref>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
